ug formularies (vidal, british national formulary)." Drug Saf 30 (2007): 1063-71[5] "Product Information. Exelon (rivastigmine)" Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[6] "Product Information. Aricept (donepezil)." Pfizer US Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.', 'Artesunate, Artemether, Pyrimethamine, Tafenoquine, Atovaquone, Proguanil, Sulfadoxine', 'Memantine, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
